    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Discretization error exceeds required level (achieved 3 vs required 2). Six factors appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. Provenance chain from claim through validation activities to foundational datasets is documented. The synthesis result node consolidating prior hemolysis literature provides contextual support for model form selection. Overall credibility evidence is sufficient to support the regulatory submission claim that CFD correctly identifies worst-case hemolysis operating conditions.",
